jj    6月考n3</blockquote><br />\n我hea學丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3231b5d0891fb276bb087a7d99a15a5f1540cc99","tid":86580,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果只係想初步試下<br />\n可以諗工聯會550蚊 12堂日文初班 <br />\n學50音同埋vocab<br />\n我上左一半覺得唔錯<br />\n平平地無壓力，而且唔似自學，自學根本睇唔明d 50音點讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 況且之後如果無興趣讀咪當平平地興趣班上完就算<br />\nBtw如果認真想讀上去考n54321當我廢up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自學左五十音，唔知依家應該點<br />\n<br />\n背，用app 做test,點填<br />\n<br />\n不過d vocab 係由零開始記，真係齋靠死記定係點<br />\n<br />\n工聯會三月先開班"},{"pid":"9f7f964d01c2aa3bdacb6d12e4477eb9f775eb0c","tid":86580,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T08:16:43.000Z","msg":"有本大家的日本語<br />\n<br />\n但係齋睇讀記就ok???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c72a88dc5a496e5464f7d667a7b44d571216cf","tid":86580,"uid":14935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T08:23:30.000Z","msg":"工聯會3月開班？ 我睇漢科都係3月開班"},{"pid":"1219f59f84763af896b82ed28e3d510e971af40c","tid":86580,"uid":14935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T08:23:58.000Z","msg":"同埋我本身都讀緊書 唔可以讀到咁多堂"},{"pid":"6247a4391c1d9fa36dcbdd3ddca7beb69ccf3e63","tid":86580,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T08:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>工聯會3月開班？ 我睇漢科都係3月開班</blockquote><br />\n春季係三月<br />\n<br />\n我都係報平日放工去，不過預進度好慢<br />\n<br />\n漢科時間係點？"},{"pid":"33922557545b6301fbd0b4f8cbc77e9f617c0b5f","tid":86580,"uid":68448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋我本身都讀緊書 唔可以讀到咁多堂</blockquote><br />\n我讀緊工聯會一個禮拜一堂1.5hour 比你參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8004bbfa750f72d102be4140ad03b453939586","tid":86580,"uid":51391,"like":