":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:42:00.000Z","msg":"自學嘅話<br />\n大家的日本語一定要另外再買文法解說（上網搵會有）、句型練習（本嘢得文法mc有答案）、標準問題集（上網有答案）<br />\n利申：日經學緊"},{"pid":"4d0a32caa13a27eb73662317bdc8c469d9d8b167","tid":86580,"uid":40124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:43:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.learnjapanese.aiyori.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.learnjapanese.aiyori.org&d=EuBWzc3B4ccnLZoBWH7bVEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=ef361cc8\" target=\"_blank\">www.learnjapanese.aiyori.org</a><br />\n完全新手想自學可以睇下"},{"pid":"18f6cda0332b6d334836b0d471a8c1ac33c9ea51","tid":86580,"uid":3900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:46:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n華東理工大學新篇日語教程，N5學到N1都得</blockquote><br />\n巴打學過？可以share 多d嗎？</blockquote><br />\n我跟呢套書學左幾年，呢間出版社配套幾齊全，除左課本仲有一系列vocab grammar listening書，排版又靚，用黎應付能力試一流</blockquote><br />\n我N4到已經好滿足 目的係可以旅遊時同日本人溝通到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nN4...我覺得唔得囉"},{"pid":"e53cb4bc61e2058aa2aff11b853494a743fca835","tid":86580,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:11:16.000Z","msg":"自學緊<br />\n之前背完50音<br />\n而家背生字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日文歌睇埋中日文字幕"},{"pid":"7818fa301a2a5aae79a8f645659cb1db87b60ee2","tid":86580,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自學緊<br />\n之前背完50音<br />\n而家背生字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日文歌睇埋中日文字幕</blockquote><br />\n生字係咪不停死記<br />\n<br />\n我睇緊d 班，最快都要三月開<br />\n<br />\n諗住報漢科<br />\n<br />\n想係呢段時間再打穩d 個底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae050c6784cc20e41fd7a15cd9bfa23f9660529","tid":86580,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:50:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自學緊<br />\n之前背完50音<br />\n而家背生字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日文歌睇埋中日文字幕</blockquote><br />\n生字係咪不停死記<br />\n<br />\n我睇緊d 班，最快都要三月開<br />\n<br />\n諗住報漢科<br />\n<br />\n想係呢段時間再打穩d 個底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係買咗半書日日背 唔想出面上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋上youtube search空中大學日語 都教得幾詳細"},{"pid":"ba1f7acdf8c0c4d222aa187d4675913847ad89ab","tid":86580,"uid":48280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自學緊<br />\n之前背完50音<br />\n而家背生字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日文歌睇埋中日文字幕</blockquote><br />\n生字係咪不停死記<br />\n<br />\n我睇緊d 班，最快都要三月開<br />\n<br />\n諗住報漢科<br />\n<br />\n想係呢段時間再打穩d 個底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係買咗半書日日背 唔想出面上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋上youtube search空中大學日語 都教得幾詳細</blockquote><br />\n想問下你地係買咩書學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未學過，見到書局有好多唔知簡邊本好"},{"pid":"2e75a6bd47cf197d05f9e7ece22a4675f1983550","tid":86580,"uid":9248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T18:30:37.000Z","msg":"買咗大家的日本語初階<br />\n頭幾個chapter已經有好多好似唔常用嘅生字<br />\n其實係咪為考試(N5)整落去?"},{"pid":"0912f750537fc68a656fa0815c5a0df2c95eab4e","tid":86580,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T18:35:55.000Z","msg":"留名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff642b958e8e707286c46b930270bab4a0d2fb0","tid":86580,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T23:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買咗大家的日本語初階<br />\n頭幾個chapter已經有好多好似唔常用嘅生字<br />\n其實係咪為考試(N5)整落去?</blockquote><br />\n我睇住本書去讀<br />\n<br />\n讀完都唔入腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daab125ba56f4c819eb54496cbedc155f9273ab1","tid":86580,"uid":3436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T02:12:52.000Z","msg":"過來人講兩句 其實好多巴打已經講左 一開始應該出去上下堂打穩個底先<br />\n五十音最基本亦都最重要 讀得唔準之後學到曉飛都好似外國人講廣東話咁奇怪<br />\n當然你可以話聽MP3/APP/UTUBE黎讀 但無人糾正發音錯哂自己都可以唔知<br />\n正如你唱K自我感覺良好 但人地聽你就走哂音五音不全<br />\n<br />\n文法 句型係3成背 7成理解 齋睇書消化唔到靠死背係好痛苦既一件事<br />\n唔好講全部動詞變化 係て型已經嚇走好多初學者<br />\n<br />\n去上下堂 學校定期有D測驗考試 逼自己溫下書 趕下進度<br />\n<br />\n打好左個底 繼續砌上去 生字/聆聽可以靠自己努力 都係靠背同工多藝熟<br />\n<br />\n同埋至少呢個階段開始識揀書睇 邊D寫得好 邊D岩自己 識得判斷而唔係靠其他人推薦 人人程度唔同 理解能力又唔同 一開始乜都唔識買本教科書返黎 全部都係得句型詞彙同練習 包保放棄得仲快"},{"pid":"9def357f0764f5fd6147dbca5f36d1b0c259a496","tid":86580,"uid":50304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T03:53:20.000Z","msg":"我都係岩岩學左兩個月 4百幾 4堂2粒鐘 學校教50音 只係教左平假 片假無學過 <br />\n50音邊只50個字 平假片假100個字了 各樣加埋仲有咬音 。 。 。 英文加埋先26個字母 日文死記就有 百幾個字母"},{"pid":"3bc01fe7282dc36f3ed696287738c463b921a227","tid":86580,"uid":43545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T04:13:09.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e9376f22dbf4b884f1a6982e0c723e85953118e0","tid":86580,"uid":3191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:17:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我跟呢套書學左幾年，呢間出版社配套幾齊全，除左課本仲有一系列vocab grammar listening書，排版又靚，用黎應付能力試一流</blockquote><br />\n我N4到已經好滿足 目的係可以旅遊時同日本人溝通到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nN4...我覺得唔得囉</blockquote><br />\nN4真係冇咩可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6a0459222442f93521c62881fab8e1055b37a8","tid":86580,"uid":54689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:28:46.000Z","msg":"日本_講座要求比較嚴格同教得認真，學費比較貴，但從功課、測驗同考試制度都睇得出間學校認真好多。期末考唔合格係真係俾錢都升唔到班架。<br />\n<br />\n第_日_ 就無咁高要求， 測驗考試都易啲，價錢平啲，但有啲老師都教得幾有心。<br />\n<br />\n另外如果想買書，又想慳啲錢，又唔介意睇殘體字嘅話：建議上樓上書店買自學書，比繁體平好多架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b857c4cd1945c25fac327d0a7cab0967baabc20","tid":86580,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:31:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係日本住左好耐，有私教日文，有冇人有興趣試下堂？</blockquote><br />\n有性趣"},{"pid":"c9c9d15221103cf655bfe940661fa0ff6503c571","tid":86580,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我跟呢套書學左幾年，呢間出版社配套幾齊全，除左課本仲有一系列vocab grammar listening書，排版又靚，用黎應付能力試一流</blockquote><br />\n我N4到已經好滿足 目的係可以旅遊時同日本人溝通到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nN4...我覺得唔得囉</blockquote><br />\nN4真係冇咩可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇你溝通的定義   問佢基本野 例如自我介紹 興趣 買賣問價錢 都仲可以  一去到深入講感受 形容物件 即刻啞左係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 :N4"},{"pid":"973a38dcc4a5aad66a0de5ff02662bd745cda58b","tid":86580,"uid":14935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nN4...我覺得唔得囉</blockquote><br />\nN4真係冇咩可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇你溝通的定義   問佢基本野 例如自我介紹 興趣 買賣問價錢 都仲可以  一去到深入講感受 形容物件 即刻啞左係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 :N4</blockquote><br />\n我都係大概咁樣算 又唔係想做日本人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09b4c1e8874f779499c66d95d2a7b64bdb11610","tid":86580,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:43:10.000Z","msg":"比我教，我收得貴出面少少但進度快幾倍<br />\n你可以用起底功能search下我點解要教日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTelegram 搵我傾<br />\n@abcccccccc"},{"pid":"1fb8a58e68e01176e0219244c381fb8490956f3c","tid":86580,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:04:01.000Z","msg":"有app同網站可以搵日本人互相交流<br />\n我自學緊 錄音講日文同比d寫日文嘅相佢哋睇 話我學得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5ab95087f528498f2f09a438cbb121ef424d0b","tid":86580,"uid":56372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:54:33.000Z","msg":"零格phone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b333f1403b0d81a6908d6772abd41c5fec5964","tid":86580,"uid":20757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有app同網站可以搵日本人互相交流<br />\n我自學緊 錄音講日文同比d寫日文嘅相佢哋睇 話我學得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n求app同網站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cec54d04ffb366c5b0eceddba8c1bec57cdeb9","tid":86580,"uid":42850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:09:28.000Z","msg":"見樓上有巴打話50音唔止五十個音 英文字母都係16隻<br />\n但係日文黎講 你學哂50音+拗音 所有字你都識讀（唔包括無標注平假名既漢字啦）<br />\n你學完26粒字母會唔會識哂所有字先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555cf877d22af86c030fda7c8eb4e003ec4d5289","tid":86580,"uid":10729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T06:26:32.000Z","msg":"第一日語學緊，都教得唔錯"},{"pid":"f5188ba5540495847875add63029446fa5b5e4dc","tid":86580,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T06:28:10.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"dd46cfa9f90c628888328386e03216d87aa7ddb6","tid":86580,"uid":43304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T06:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一日語學緊，都教得唔錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日經定第一好?<br />\n由零學起"},{"pid":"06927f6a5f6ef321ac4ed2467de577f21f077c23","tid":86580,"uid":29246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T06:40:00.000Z","msg":"LM 自學完五十音 但係語法真係好難好多野背 い&amp;な的形容詞都未背完"},{"pid":"04a2430adf3d3990cb9f3a8e2a57fcb616c3f5d6","tid":86580,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T06:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>自學緊<br />\n之前背完50音<br />\n而家背生字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日文歌睇埋中日文字幕</blockquote><br />\n生字係咪不停死記<br />\n<br />\n我睇緊d 班，最快都要三月開<br />\n<br />\n諗住報漢科<br />\n<br />\n想係呢段時間再打穩d 個底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係買咗半書日日背 唔想出面上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋上youtube search空中大學日語 都教得幾詳細</blockquote><br />\n我都睇緊空中大學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽個台灣人學左空中大學啲野已經N5  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5502395b602dbae78ced54051c544826c9493217","tid":86580,"uid":43304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T07:54:36.000Z","msg":"初學嘅話<br />\n日經定第一好?"},{"pid":"c87af84ab7feabe001789f00672b52d260f01b04","tid":86580,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:22:36.000Z","msg":"十年前係日本文化協會讀過<br />\n幾乎一兩堂要測驗<br />\n自己就無咩心機溫書<br />\n讀左一季第二季無咩人讀就無讀落去<br />\n<br />\n今次再的起心肝<br />\n揀左第一日語<br />\n叫做好輕鬆無壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係興趣班咁<br />\n<br />\n其實都係睇你想人地迫你讀定自在咁讀啦<br />\n我自己選擇後者<br />\n平時好懶連功課都唔做<br />\n升到班但自覺日文無咩進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225b6899bdb845390df9bf365ce12169075c6de3","tid":86580,"uid":34634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T19:47:57.000Z","msg":"幾年前喺pasona學過，自己幾鍾意佢嘅教法<br />\n小班教學，同埋多課堂活動（會話為主）<br />\n唔知係咪因為日資，都幾多唔同國籍嘅同學<br />\n上堂多會話練習（算係造句練習？），同埋間中有啲活動同日本人交流<br />\n<br />\n依家長時間唔喺香港，用japanesepod101自修多<br />\n出年可能會去日本WH"},{"pid":"c7ae0c8798a5fa00042036978211185f1f7c8a08","tid":86580,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T19:08:14.000Z","msg":"呢排我都係每日背生字<br />\n買多咗本文法書教句型<br />\n但一睇n5試題淨係識少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗緊好唔好買音速日語 見佢有個60日考到n4嘅方法<br />\n而家學得好慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae84c6